---
layout: base.njk
title: Evidence Dashboard
description: "Public anonymised evidence dashboard — I-PACE owner data on battery health, recalls and outcomes."
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Public Evidence</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Evidence Dashboard</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">Anonymised, aggregate data submitted voluntarily by I-PACE owners.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section section--sm bg-muted">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="callout callout--warning">
      <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
      <div class="callout__content">
        <p class="callout__title">Placeholder data — collection not yet active</p>
        <p>This dashboard shows the intended layout and structure. Real data collection has not yet begun.
        All figures shown are illustrative samples only. When live, data will be submitted voluntarily
        by owners and will be marked by verification level.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
          <a href="/methodology/">Read the full methodology →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section section--sm">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-8); font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted);">
      <strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Data disclaimer:</strong>
      Data is submitted voluntarily by owners. Entries are marked by verification level:
      self-reported, document supplied, reviewed, duplicate-checked, or excluded from public statistics.
      Public figures are anonymised and aggregated. Sample bias may apply — owners with issues are
      more likely to submit data.
    </div>

    <!-- Stat cards -->
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Summary statistics</h2>
    <div class="grid grid--4" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Owners contributed</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Vehicles with HV battery work</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—%</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Average reported SoH</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—%</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Recall completion rate</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">H570/H571/H572</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Vehicles outside battery warranty</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">8yr / 100k miles</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Repeat battery issues</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">— days</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Average days off road</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—%</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Loan car provided</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-card__value">—</span>
        <span class="stat-card__label">Goodwill / payment issues</span>
        <span class="stat-card__note">Sample data</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Chart panels -->
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Charts and distributions</h2>
    <div class="grid" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">

      <div class="chart-panel">
        <h3 class="chart-panel__title">State of Health distribution</h3>
        <div class="bar-chart" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder SoH distribution chart">
          <div class="bar-chart__row">
            <span class="bar-chart__label">90–100%</span>
            <div class="bar-chart__track"><div class="bar-chart__fill" style="width:35%"></div></div>
            <span class="bar-chart__value">35%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-chart__row">
            <span class="bar-chart__label">80–90%</span>
            <div class="bar-chart__track"><div class="bar-chart__fill" style="width:40%"></div></div>
            <span class="bar-chart__value">40%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-chart__row">
            <span class="bar-chart__label">70–80%</span>
            <div class="bar-chart__track"><div class="bar-chart__fill" style="width:18%"></div></div>
            <span class="bar-chart__value">18%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bar-chart__row">
            <span class="bar-chart__label">&lt;70%</span>
            <div class="bar-chart__track"><div class="bar-chart__fill" style="width:7%"></div></div>
            <span class="bar-chart__value">7%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-top:var(--space-3);margin-bottom:0;">Illustrative data only</p>
      </div>

      <div class="chart-panel">
        <h3 class="chart-panel__title">Model year distribution</h3>
        <div class="bar-chart" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder model year distribution chart">
